snippet.title: Galaxseed Demo
snippet.description:
Roaring Cat Game's GalaxSeed gameplay demo for Kentucky Fried Pixel bundle: https://itch.io/b/122/kentucky-fried-pixels

This title blossomed from its original debut in LibGDX jam: https://itch.io/jam/libgdxjam titled, Planttary Planter.
